<h2><a name='sect0' href='#toc0'>Name</a></h2>
<b>MPI_File_iwrite_shared</b> - Writes a file using the shared file
pointer (nonblocking, noncollective).
<p>
<p>
<p>
<h2><a name='sect1' href='#toc1'>Syntax</a></h2>
